The paper proposes a new method for speeding up the inference of deep neural networks, which is a common problem in the fields of machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
